			"value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n      <strong>School:</strong>&nbsp;enchantment&nbsp;(compulsion)&nbsp;[mind-affecting];\n    <br>\n    <strong>Level:</strong>&nbsp;Bard 2, Sorcerer 3, Wizard 3;\n    <strong>Domain:</strong>&nbsp;Charm 4;\n    \n    \n    \n    <br>\n    <strong>Components:</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n    \n      <strong>Casting Time:</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Range:</strong>&nbsp;touch<br>\n    \n    <strong>Target:</strong>&nbsp;creature touched<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;10 min./level<br>\n    \n        <strong>Saving Throw:</strong>&nbsp;Will negates (harmless)\n        <br>\n        <strong>Spell Resistance:</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  \n\n\n<p>\nThis spell imbues a single creature with great bravery and morale in battle. The target gains a +2 morale bonus on attack rolls, saves, and skill checks.\n</p>\n<hr/>\n\n\n\n</div>\n"
